This is the TouchPoint-FCC repo — a script library for TouchPoint church 
management software.

Context:
- TouchPoint is a hosted SaaS platform with a built-in Python/SQL/HTML shell
- Scripts are copy/pasted manually into TouchPoint to run — nothing deploys automatically
- Database is Microsoft SQL Server, managed by TouchPoint (hosted)
- No external DB connections — TouchPoint handles all DB access internally
- Small writes/updates occur occasionally but majority of scripts are read-only

Structure:
- Reports/          — Python + SQL scripts for data reports
- Dashboards/       — HTML/CSS for UX/UI visuals
- SQLqueries/       — Standalone SQL queries
- Widgets/          — Embeddable HTML/CSS widgets
- HTMLsnippets/     — Small HTML components for emails and registration forms
- OnEnrollScripts/  — Actions triggered automatically during registration/enrollment
- _templates/       — Always copy from here when starting something ons:
- Top level folders: Capitalized words (Reports/, Dashboards/, etc.)
- Subfolders and script folders: camelCase (monthlyGivingReport/)
- Script files: camelCase matching folder name (monthlyGivingReport.py)

Rules:
- Every script folder must have a README.md
- SQL scripts that write data must clearly mark write risk in README
- Never hardcode names, IDs, or any real data in scripts
- All new scripts copied from _templates/ first
- Commit using Conventional Commits format
